# How to install system requirements

## Gnu make

Download the tarball from the [GNU ftp](http://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/make/) and follow instructions in the `INSTALL` file.

## Rust and Cargo

### Linux, macOS, or other Unix-like operating system

The following command installs Rust and Cargo.

`curl --proto '=https' --tlsv1.2 -sSf https://sh.rustup.rs | sh`

### Windows

Download and run [rustup-init.exe](https://static.rust-lang.org/rustup/dist/i686-pc-windows-gnu/rustup-init.exe).
